biography: Stefan is a data engineer and works at Covestro in a newly established data office. He has four years of experience working on a variety of data platforms, ranging from classic ETL pipelines and data warehousing to near–real-time stream processing. Before moving into data engineering, he completed a PhD in physics, where he felt in love with Python and working with data. Since then he is always curious to learn new things and share what he has learned with others.
